WHY GPL v3?

This project is for the Bitcoin and open-source community.
The GPL ensures that:

  • Anyone can use, study, modify and distribute this software freely.
  • Any derivative work or fork MUST also be released under the GPL.
  • No one can take this project, make it proprietary, and close the source.

That aligns with Bitcoin's values of openness, transparency, and
permissionless innovation. Forks are welcome — just keep them free.
